~ final1
[wait=3]The sky turns red. The Culling has oficially begun. 
Late in the evening, as you cleanse your final item of the day, you hear screams coming from outside. 
You watch through the window. You see people gathered around a body, near the gate. 
Through a small gap, you're able to see Duncan's body, laying on the ground, deformed and dry, as the Culling sucks the final breath of life out of his body.
They almost made it. But the Goddess got to him first. 
It's the first time ever that the Cullings have taken someone's life inside of the village. 
Sarah's crying. Her fate is still in question. => END 

~ final2
[wait=3]The sky turns red. The Culling has oficially begun. 
The Elders' lackeys found Duncan and Sarah. They sentenced Duncan to death for heresy. 
Late in the evening, as you cleanse your final item of the day, you hear screams coming from outside. 
You watch through the window. You see people gathered around a body, near the sacrificial altar. 
Through a small gap, you're able to see Duncan's body, laying on the ground, deformed and dry, as the Culling sucks the final breath of life out of his body. 
He didn't make it to his execution. The Goddess got to him first. 
It's the first time ever that the Cullings have taken someone's life inside of the village. 
Sarah's crying. Her fate is still in question. => END 


=> END

